ed from April 7 to June 23, 2019.\n\n==Characters==\n;{{Nihongo|Yuki|\u30e6\u30ad|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Kana Hanazawa]]|Lindsay Seidel}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\">{{cite web|url=https://www.funimation.com/forum/topic/18076/master-thread-afterlost-dubbed|title=[MASTER THREAD] AFTERLOST Dub Cast|website=Funimation|publisher=Funimation|accessdate=29 April 2019}}</ref>\n\n;{{Nihongo|Takuya|\u30bf\u30af\u30e4|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Tomokazu Sugita]]|[[Jason Liebrecht]]}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Akira|\u30a2\u30ad\u30e9|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Yuichi Nakamura (voice actor)|Yuichi Nakamura]]|Orion Pitts}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Soma|\u30bd\u30a6\u30de|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Ayaka Asai]]|Mikaela Krantz}}<ref name=\"Premiere\">{{cite web |last1=Hodgkins |first1=Crystalyn |title=Sh\u014dmetsu Toshi Anime Reveals More Cast, 4th Teaser Visual |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-09-28/shometsu-toshi-anime-reveals-more-cast-4th-teaser-visual/.137429 |website=Anime News Network |accessdate=September 28, 2018 |date=September 28, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Eiji|\u30a8\u30a4\u30b8|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Tarusuke Shingaki|Kyle Igneczi}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Kikyo|\u30ad\u30ad\u30e7\u30a6|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Aimi (actress)|Aimi]]|[[Caitlin Glass]]}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Geek|\u30ae\u30fc\u30af|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Taisuke Nishimura|Tyson Rinehart}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Yumiko|\u30e6\u30df\u30b3|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Mitsuki Nakae|Dawn M. Bennett}}<ref name=\"anime\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Kota|\u30b3\u30a6\u30bf|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Makoto Takahashi]]|Stephen Fu}}<ref name=\"staff\">{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-08-09/shometsu-toshi-anime-teaser-reveals-more-cast-staff-kenji-kawai-music/.135315 |title=Sh\u014dmetsu Toshi Anime's Teaser Reveals More Cast, Staff, Kenji Kawai's Music |last=Loo |first=Egan |date=August 9, 2018 |website=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=August 10, 2018 }}</ref><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Homura|\u30db\u30e0\u30e9|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Haruka Shamoto|[[Michelle Rojas]]}}<ref name=\"staff\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Nami|\u30ca\u30df|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Emiri Iwai|Kristen McGuire}}<ref name=\"staff\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Haruka|\u30cf\u30eb\u30ab|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Hina Suguta|Amanda Gish}}<ref name=\"staff\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Rena|\u30ec\u30ca|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Aguri \u014cnishi]]|Kasi Hollowell}}<ref name=\"staff\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Yua|\u30e6\u30a2|}}\n:{{Voiced by|Hikari Sonoyama|Megan Shipman}}<ref name=\"staff\" /><ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Ry\u014dko|\u30ea\u30e7\u30a6\u30b3|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Tomoyo Kurosawa]]}}<ref name=\"Premiere\" /> (Japanese); Mallorie Rodak (English)<ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Tsubasa|\u30c4\u30d0\u30b5|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Nobunaga Shimazaki]]|Alejandro Saab}}<ref name=\"more-cast\">{{cite web |last1=Sherman |first1=Jennifer |title=Sh\u014dmetsu Toshi Anime Reveals More Cast, 5th Teaser Visual |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-10-29/shometsu-toshi-anime-reveals-more-cast-5th-teaser-visual/.138776 |website=Anime News Network |accessdate=October 29, 2018 |date=October 29, 2018}}</ref>\n\n;{{Nihongo|Yoshiaki|\u30e8\u30b7\u30a2\u30ad|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Yoshitsugu Matsuoka]]}}<ref name=\"more-cast\" /> (Japanese); [[Jerry Jewell]] (English)<ref name=\"dub cast\" />\n\n;{{Nihongo|Suzuna|\u30b9\u30ba\u30ca|}}\n:{{Voiced by|[[Ayane Sakura]]|Brianna Roberts}}<ref name=\"april\">{{cite web |last1=Sherman |first1=Jennifer |title=Sh\u014dmetsu Toshi Anime Reveals Promo Video, Visual, Cast, April Premiere |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-12-26/shometsu-toshi-anime-reveals-promo-video-visual-cast-april-pr